rding to senior Senate staff working on the bill, the hotline typically takes on an internally agreed upon time limit of up to 24 hours or sometimes longer, instead of the alleged 6 hours. The bill thus has not been passed.<br />\n<br />\nThe future is yet to come. May all of us stand valiant and true."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T04:54:53.000Z","msg":"what... rumour only <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> wtf"},{"pid":"da61d7334e2957d14f9b72b19f0cfb3366dafdff","tid":1721850,"uid":169665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T05:01:33.000Z","msg":"尋晚已經話要打暈佢<br />\n燈一燈又拖到下個禮拜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48a13a62e8cdbddfe932cf742d9003afa9aa9704","tid":1721850,"uid":241628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T05:03:48.000Z","msg":"屌 出少句聲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2430e1a244edf10a5ad5abe1c8afe9daca89cf5d","tid":1721850,"uid":282118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T05:08:38.000Z","msg":"又燈撚埋我"},{"pid":"b10fbc417409c7000716ea6e2ffa1514cbe33832","tid":1721850,"uid":174060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T05:24:14.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 點解仲未有人毒撚啞佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"353840eeaea28b277547f3201874cd08e829e0e2","tid":1721850,"uid":144522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bdcd8168da5bb9880737b6d4304641dd2432bcf7","tid":1721850,"uid":81270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3cf23780c9b54992714efa0dc8f4730a14d2a35","tid":1721850,"uid":144522,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T18:49:58.000Z","msg":"要破燈啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:49:56.000Z","msg":"柒咗啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:11:31.000Z","msg":"咁撚樣都有得燈  <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/i